# Anserini: Regressions for [TREC-3 Monolingual Spanish](https://trec.nist.gov/pubs/trec3/t3_proceedings.html)

This page documents regression experiments for [TREC-3 ad hoc retrieval (Monolingual Spanish)](https://trec.nist.gov/pubs/trec3/t3_proceedings.html).
The description of the document collection can be found on the [TREC data page](https://trec.nist.gov/data/docs_noneng.html).

The exact configurations for these regressions are stored in [this YAML file](../src/main/resources/regression/trec3-es.yaml).
Note that this page is automatically generated from [this template](../src/main/resources/docgen/templates/trec3-es.template) as part of Anserini's regression pipeline, so do not modify this page directly; modify the template instead.

## Indexing

Typical indexing command:

```
