```

The collection comprises the Mexican newspaper El Norte, from [LDC2000T51 (TREC Spanish)](https://catalog.ldc.upenn.edu/LDC2000T51).
Inside the LDC2000T51 distribution, there should be a directory named `infosel_data`, which contains 194 files.
The path above `/path/to/trec4-es/` should point to this `infosel_data/` directory.
The collection contains 57,868 documents.

For additional details, see explanation of [common indexing options](common-indexing-options.md).

